        email - - the email of the user that has entered or left the building
        employeeID - - the employee ID of the user in the business
        deviceID - - the device or location in which the person gained access
        name - - the name of the person
        surname - - the surname of the person
        timestamp - - the time the user gained access to the building
        day - - the day number to validate performance in which one can check logs easier
